text:
Here you go, ready whenever you are.
Okay, two minutes from now.
Today, it's the usual Hiori, isn't it?

Oh...! Even though the outfit is different,
the stage is still the "usual".

Both the outfit and the stage aren't the
"usual" from before, but I feel much calmer.

I can send you off without any worries.
Give it your all out there, just like you always do.
